# User allowlist.
# Each entry maps one player to their auth credentials.
#
# Provision a new user:  ../scripts/provision-user.sh <uid> "Display Name"
# That creates /srv/df/users/<uid>/save/, appends an entry here, and prints the access key.
#
# After adding users to a running deployment, reload without restarting:
#   docker compose kill -s SIGHUP session-manager
